# Retired OCR Gerontikon per-letter pages -> the facsimile at /fathers/gerontiko/
# Use a placeholder (:slug), NOT a splat: a splat also matched the facsimile
# page's own URL /fathers/gerontiko/ and ping-ponged with Astro's trailing-slash
# redirect (infinite loop). :slug requires a segment, so the bare index is never
# matched. Cover both the slashed and unslashed old letter URLs; the destination
# keeps the trailing slash so it lands on the page without a further bounce.
/fathers/gerontiko/:slug/  /fathers/gerontiko/  301
/fathers/gerontiko/:slug   /fathers/gerontiko/  301
